h23 y400 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">determined to ruin God&apos;s lovely creation. </div><div class="t m4fd x8f h23 y251 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the book </div><div class="t m218 xaf h23 y251 ff7 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Education, </div><div class="t m146 x19 h23 y4b9 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 17, we read that &quot;every human being, </div><div class="t m13b x3f h23 y2a8 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">created in the image of God, is endowed with a power akin to that of </div><div class="t m4fe x3f h23 y2a9 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Creator—individuality, power to think and to do.&quot; How have </div><div class="t m4ff x32 h23 y253 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Satan&apos;s efforts undermined your individuality, your power to think </div><div class="t m42c x3f h23 y254 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to do? As you study this week&apos;s lesson, ask yourself this question </div><div class="t m500 x3f h23 y4ba ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as it relates to you personally. But don&apos;t just leave it there. Also ask </div><div class="t m282 x3f h23 y256 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">yourself how you can resist Satan&apos;s efforts to make sure you are not </div><div class="t m29e x3f h23 y4bb ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reflecting your Creator. It is a battle for the human heart and destiny. </div><div class="t m501 x3f h23 y4bc ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Satan&apos;s plan is to plunge people further into their fallen state, leading </div><div class="t m8e x3f h23 y4bd ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them to their eternal destruction. God&apos;s plan is to help them regain </div><div class="t m493 x3f h23 y258 ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what they had lost and ultimately be restored to His image. </div><div class="t m190 x48 h23 y25a ff4 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">46 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
